  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Taverna is a first person adventure in a world of online  taverns. Create and customize your own locale or explore others with up to 16 players (per lobby). Earn gold, complete quests, unlock items and have fun with role-play.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your tavern</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paint </strong>walls, <strong>add forniture</strong>, <strong>lights</strong>, and <strong>decorations </strong>to create a unique atmosphere. Every detail in your tavern is yours to customize, making it a welcoming place for friends and fellow adventurers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Voice chat!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Communicate vocally</strong> with other players in fun and interactive ways. Organize stand-up comedy nights or just spend the night with your friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Freedom to create</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Express yourself</strong> in a variety of ways: <strong>painting, decorating, playing instruments</strong>, and <strong>customizing the environment.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get immersed in a fantasy world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a cozy, fantasy tavern</strong> straight out of your favorite story or video game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Other features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from between more than <strong>15 roles</strong>. Whether you decide to be a <strong>cook</strong>, a <strong>bard</strong>, or simply a <strong>traveler</strong>, this choice will shape your role-play experience in Taverna by adding a special tag on top of your head.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn gold and use it to <strong>unlock unique items </strong>to progress your tavern. <strong>Chairs</strong>, <strong>pots</strong>, <strong>books</strong>, <strong>cutlery</strong>, <strong>ingredients</strong>, <strong>paints </strong>and so much more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in a variety of games and social activities, making every session unique. From classic tavern games to hosting themed events, Taverna is an ideal space for role-play gatherings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a new level of interactivity with <strong>physics</strong>. <strong>Throw</strong>, <strong>flip</strong>, <strong>eat</strong>, <strong>drink</strong>, <strong>pose</strong>, <strong>pick up</strong> and much more… every object can be used in various ways, often with unexpected results.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete quests to unlock new roles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Taverna is a first person adventure in a world of online  taverns. Create and customize your own locale or explore others with up to 16 players (per lobby). Earn gold, complete quests, unlock items and have fun with role-play.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your tavern</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paint </strong>walls, <strong>add forniture</strong>, <strong>lights</strong>, and <strong>decorations </strong>to create a unique atmosphere. Every detail in your tavern is yours to customize, making it a welcoming place for friends and fellow adventurers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Voice chat!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Communicate vocally</strong> with other players in fun and interactive ways. Organize stand-up comedy nights or just spend the night with your friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Freedom to create</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Express yourself</strong> in a variety of ways: <strong>painting, decorating, playing instruments</strong>, and <strong>customizing the environment.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get immersed in a fantasy world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a cozy, fantasy tavern</strong> straight out of your favorite story or video game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Other features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from between more than <strong>15 roles</strong>. Whether you decide to be a <strong>cook</strong>, a <strong>bard</strong>, or simply a <strong>traveler</strong>, this choice will shape your role-play experience in Taverna by adding a special tag on top of your head.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn gold and use it to <strong>unlock unique items </strong>to progress your tavern. <strong>Chairs</strong>, <strong>pots</strong>, <strong>books</strong>, <strong>cutlery</strong>, <strong>ingredients</strong>, <strong>paints </strong>and so much more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in a variety of games and social activities, making every session unique. From classic tavern games to hosting themed events, Taverna is an ideal space for role-play gatherings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a new level of interactivity with <strong>physics</strong>. <strong>Throw</strong>, <strong>flip</strong>, <strong>eat</strong>, <strong>drink</strong>, <strong>pose</strong>, <strong>pick up</strong> and much more… every object can be used in various ways, often with unexpected results.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete quests to unlock new roles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
